data.name: Label11.Text
data.value:
Turn on music: Switches the music on and the Sound effects off
Turn on SFX: Switches the music off and the sound effects on
Change background colour: Allows you to change the background colour from the default of black
Difficulty: Changes the difficulty, the higher the difficulty the more often the invaders will shoot
Game Pace: Speeds up or slows down the invaders movement speed
Clear Highscores: Clears the saved highscore list from the disk CANNOT BE UNDONE

data.name: Label13.Text
data.value:
The invaders move side to side on the screen till the leftmost or rightmost hits the edge they then drop down one row and move in the opposite direction.
The more invaders you kill the faster the remaining ones move.

data.name: Label6.Text
data.value:
You start with 3 lives, Remaining lives are displayed in the bottom left corner of the screen.
You lose a life everytime: An invader's shot hits your ship without an active shield A UFO's shot hits your ship
Game over occurs if; Your ship is touched by and invader, Atleast one invader makes it to the bottom of the screen, or if you run out of lives

data.name: Label4.Text
data.value:
A Speed power up increases the movement speed of your ship for 10 seconds
A Multi-shot power up allows rapid fire of up to 5 shots at once for 10 seconds
A Shield power up makes your ship invincible to enemy shots for 7.5 seconds Note: One shot from the UFO will remove the shield regardless of remaining time
